<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11351</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20850</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>深夜，一个哨兵在一个旧军事基地里巡逻。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20851</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26100</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“晚上真安静啊。”哨兵自言自语，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30601</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我还是去办公室睡一会儿吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40600</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哨兵走到一栋楼房的拐角，大吃一惊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40601</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47827</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“坏了！”他叫道，“一辆坦克被偷了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47828</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53730</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太好了！”特勒尔说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53731</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56766</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不用在教室里上课！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56767</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64016</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>学校的花园里，罗西和朋友们正在帮格林老师的忙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64017</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68266</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“早上好！同学们！”格林老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68267</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71266</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天会特别好玩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71267</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74965</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个人都得有手套和铲子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74966</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81250</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西和朋友们拿到了他们的园艺工具。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81251</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克笑了。“我等不及把自己弄脏了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92751</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我这里有很多花种和菜种。”格林老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们可以选自己想种的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103001</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>只要付出时间和爱心，这些植物就会长大！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉选了向日葵种子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110500</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我喜欢向日葵。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110501</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113751</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它们又大又阳光。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119001</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我喜欢午餐的时候，吃新鲜的蔬菜。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122500</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要种胡萝卜和生菜。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122501</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125465</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克一脸不在乎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125466</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131684</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁要关心蔬菜！我只是喜欢挖土！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137934</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把铲子插进土里，挖出一些土。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144434</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他捡起一条蠕动的小蚯蚓。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150683</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真酷！”杰克拿起蚯蚓给朋友们看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150684</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155567</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呃......”特勒尔说，“把它拿开！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159817</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真恶心，杰克。”玛拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163138</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“蚯蚓很可爱。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163139</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“而且，它可以让土壤变得更肥沃。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172360</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉和罗西挖土。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172361</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我等不及看向日葵开花了。”玛拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176836</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181794</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你得先把它们种上！”罗西笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181795</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186756</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们知道这个花园少了什么吗？”杰克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186757</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188901</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一个水池！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193684</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望是个有青蛙的水池。”玛拉说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有几只乌龟。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202701</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许火箭女孩儿能帮我们挖一个大水池！”特勒尔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205634</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西转了转眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿太忙了，特勒尔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211742</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她没时间挖水池。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211743</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔耸了耸肩。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，罗西的手表响了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224751</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西离开了朋友们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231001</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她按了一下手表上的按钮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234084</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“布洛姆市长。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235716</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有什么事吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235717</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239424</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿！”布洛姆市长说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239425</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242867</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有人抢劫了美罗城中央银行！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246123</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别担心，市长！”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246124</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很快就到！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>